                     >
                






    
    
        
    



                





        <h3 class="heading">自動止盈</h3>

<p>根據您的盈利目標設置<strong>限價指令</strong>，我們將會在價格達到您選擇的水準時為您平倉。</p>


                
            </div><div class="clearfix"></div>

        
        
    </div>
</div></div>
<div class="new-content-component section">


















